{"tid":1238840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重奪老人家的一票！！Part Time乖孫全面進場！！","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T01:28:06.000Z","uid":134589,"like":1374,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"e73a33aecc9794f7299c6d784281b6f0334a6688","tid":1238840,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"民建聯出動到派餅仔同掌心雷去引一班老人家投自己一票<br />\n我諗左好耐可以點樣令佢地投返民主派<br />\n又唔可以阻住班老人家去投票 守住唔比民建聯又可能比人話暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下諗下　記得之前有位巴打提出左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Part Time 乖孫</span>呢個概念<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/441616/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/441616/page/1</a><br />\n冇錯 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係愛</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">愛可以感染咁多位老人家相信我地 投代表民主既一邊!</span><br />\n咁多位巴打絲打 係時候盡顯你地既孝心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好孝敬下老人家<br />\n多D關懷 多D愛心<br />\n<strong>得閒送下禮物仔<br />\n唱下歌 搞下笑 變下魔術<br />\n哄佢地開心</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等佢地當左你係佢個孫一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n咁就會聽晒你話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家可以當自己係義工<br />\n加入義工團體</span></span><br />\n咁就可以入各大老人院 孝敬老人家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9fbd87082e63a71433f38b14773edd30b50e83","tid":1238840,"uid":134589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"492abbed17a84e2361dee27ed17c0ffa5f0b7504","tid":1238840,"uid":199893,"like":270,"dislike":0,"score":270,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:16:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n之前啲人都幾有大局觀"},{"pid":"21e1c2faef46b9748432a4545585425118a20c4a","tid":1238840,"uid":258927,"like":83,"dislike":1,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4rguvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4rguvu.jpg&h=f7216136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n# 生於亂世 有種責任<br />\n# 求share出fb/ig/tg/wtsapp"},{"pid":"287174bb3fa62229e975bb2a7802faed3177d08c","tid":1238840,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"PUSH比多D人睇"},{"pid":"1f8bb9a49dc0749d6d157ba5742168de9dcf6a95","tid":1238840,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d238fe340b559812da32c16010d8c6e00cec08","tid":1238840,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561d67ebb2323135e59b8cf68906528f4d7f0e69","tid":1238840