會on99咁好慢 凌晨時份會好啲 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ecdd3241\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=201cf2cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=fc92b80e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=2f047226\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=8a5766b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=d298feb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=5f405f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"e37fab2cac6537c3a9d8318b66b32e3e74cc5b08","tid":1238840,"uid":203858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e73a33aecc9794f7299c6d784281b6f0334a6688","tid":1238840,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"民建聯出動到派餅仔同掌心雷去引一班老人家投自己一票<br />\n我諗左好耐可以點樣令佢地投返民主派<br />\n又唔可以阻住班老人家去投票 守住唔比民建聯又可能比人話暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下諗下　記得之前有位巴打提出左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Part Time 乖孫</span>呢個概念<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/441616/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/441616/page/1</a><br />\n冇錯 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係愛</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">愛可以感染咁多位老人家相信我地 投代表民主既一邊!</span><br />\n咁多位巴打絲打 係時候盡顯你地既孝心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好孝敬下老人家<br />\n多D關懷 多D愛心<br />\n<strong>得閒送下禮物仔<br />\n唱下歌 搞下笑 變下魔術<br />\n哄佢地開心</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等佢地當左你係佢個孫一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n咁就會聽晒你話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家可以當自己係義工<br />\n加入義工團體</span></span><br />\n咁就可以入各大老人院 孝敬老人家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed81f08124c065d713464fa0093250433d4a0a0d","tid":1238840,"uid":190164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d21bcf361d8eab3bb64a8a7debf6cd539e7f6e3a","tid":1238840,"uid":134589,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3ab466f02256967