e":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"如果有d深藍既父母 講極唔聽<br />\n就預早plan定請佢地兩老果幾日去旅行<br />\n唔係香港就投唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又幫到香港 又孝順埋父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f180a8132f23219c115b2ddecbdb46aa411ccc9","tid":1238840,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b028330fcab2dabefad290a3755c705ea6ad47","tid":1238840,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">由關懷開始</span>"},{"pid":"ef9e288b446dfca7cf12280de600704aaef1b518","tid":1238840,"uid":261756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e73a33aecc9794f7299c6d784281b6f0334a6688","tid":1238840,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"民建聯出動到派餅仔同掌心雷去引一班老人家投自己一票<br />\n我諗左好耐可以點樣令佢地投返民主派<br />\n又唔可以阻住班老人家去投票 守住唔比民建聯又可能比人話暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下諗下　記得之前有位巴打提出左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Part Time 乖孫</span>呢個概念<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/441616/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/441616/page/1</a><br />\n冇錯 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係愛</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">愛可以感染咁多位老人家相信我地 投代表民主既一邊!</span><br />\n咁多位巴打絲打 係時候盡顯你地既孝心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好好孝敬下老人家<br />\n多D關懷 多D愛心<br />\n<strong>得閒送下禮物仔<br />\n唱下歌 搞下笑 變下魔術<br />\n哄佢地開心</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等佢地當左你係佢個孫一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n咁就會聽晒你話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家可以當自己係義工<br />\n加入義工團體</span></span><br />\n咁就可以入各大老人院 孝敬老人家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"可以唔要錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198674d824d882e1ffacc97ae377ce4c54394c7c","tid":1238840,"uid":169264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f318212567f85bf607358bb7deb25cd5d68640c7","tid":1238840,"uid":2373,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:25:57.000Z","msg":"直接幫佢哋取消選民登記資格好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"如果係去老人院既話好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲老人院會幫手種票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲廢老管理層會車啲老人家去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個